sequenceDiagram
    participant CP as Charge Point (OCTT)
    participant CS as Central System (SUT)

    Note over CP,CS: TC_043_1_CSMS: Send Local Authorization List - NotSupported
    Note over CP,CS: Table 157, Section 3.14.2, Page 136/176
